denominations.name: SALE: DC Comics: Batman Luminart Light

text:
12" tall illuminating wall art featuring classic Batman cover artwork! Dual powered by either USB or battery, this iconic Batman comic book cover artwork is a must have piece of collectable fan memorabilia, featuring the Caped Crusader and his arch nemesis the Joker in a timeless classic image. Measuring 20cm x 30cm (approx. 8x12in) the light-up canvas can be free-standing or wall-mounted depending on preference, and comes with a USB cable included.

Alternatively, the light can be powered by 3 x AAA batteries (not included). Batman is the legendary comic book hero from DC Comics. First appearing in Detective Comics in 1939, he has since gone on to become a global icon of popular culture, featuring in blockbuster movies such as Batman Begins, The Dark Knight, and Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice, as well as countless TV versions, graphic novels, and video games like Arkham Knight.

Hugely popular with comic book fans around the world, DC Comics is responsible for creating many of the best loved characters in pop culture history, including Batman, Superman, and Wonder Woman among others, as well as popular crime fighting teams such as The Justice League and Suicide Squad. The Batman Luminart is an officially licensed DC Comics product.
name: SALE: DC Comics: Batman Luminart Light
